casebody.data:
BUCKMASTER v. DIRECTOR OF PATUXENT INSTITUTION [App. No. 35,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided October 19, 1964.

Before Henderson, C. J., and Prescott, Marbury, SybeRT and Oppenheimer, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Dorsey in the court below.

Application denied.
